LAMMPS (30 Mar 2026)
OMP_NUM_THREADS environment is not set. Defaulting to 1 thread.
  using 1 OpenMP thread(s) per MPI task

# ------------------ Initialization ------------------
units           metal
boundary        p p p
atom_style      atomic

# ------------------ Geometry Generation -------------
# Silicon diamond cubic lattice constant is 5.431 Angstroms

variable pwd_path getenv PWD

variable structure_file string ../structures/si_structure.txt

read_data ../structures/si_structure.txt
Reading data file ...
  orthogonal box = (0 0 0) to (16.29 16.29 16.29)
  1 by 1 by 1 MPI processor grid
  reading atoms ...
  216 atoms
  read_data CPU = 0.001 seconds

# ------------------ Interatomic Potential -----------
# Using the standard Stillinger-Weber (SW) potential
pair_style      sw
pair_coeff      * * ../potentials/Si.sw Si
Reading sw potential file ../potentials/Si.sw with DATE: 2007-06-11


# ------------------ Compute -----------------
compute eng all pe/atom 	# a variable named 'eng' is defined to store the potential energy for each atom
compute eatoms all reduce sum c_eng  #a variable named 'eatoms' is defined to store the sum of all 'eng' values
compute new all temp


# ------------------ Energy Minimization -------------
# Relax the structure to remove any initial overlapping/strain
thermo          10
thermo_style    custom step temp pe press vol

minimize 1.0e-6 1.0e-6 5000 10000
